@node "Instructions" "Instructions"

               Intructions

   This little utility assign your programms, generating a script.
 It also includes an option to create these scripts, where you ca make
 your assign, and the posibility to load the programm using only one file.
 There is also an option for adding assigns to your User-startup.

   To create a normal assign, without creating a file, you just have to
 inset the name of the prog ( ex. "Sources:" ), and then insert the path
 where the program can be found. There is the posibility to push a buttom
 with a sign like this "¶" It opens a requester where you can insert the 
 path more easy, may the name or the pathname is too long for the box, but
 with this requester you will have no problem. If you want to generate a 
 script, just do the same as above, insert first the name of the executable,
 and after that you must choose where you want the script being safed. 
 After that click on "create" and thats it.
 Adding assigns to your User-Startup is the same as above just choose 
 "Addind to User" and thats it.

    There will apear 2 button asking for "another assign" or "Proceed" that
 means that if you need to create more assigns just click on another one, if
 you finish, than click on proceed.
 If you choose to add the assign(s) to your user-Startup, that means that it 
 will generate the next script:

 ;BEGIN Commentary
 (Assign...)
 ;END Commentary

@endnode

@node "Install" "Install"

            How to Install

        You only have to execute the installer and follow
    the instructons.
@endnode

@node "Features" "Features"

            Features

  This lovely Prog can:

     * Temporaly Assigns (after a reset they are gone)

     * Scripts where you can do your assigns and then load
      y the programm

     * Add Assigns to your User-Startup

  And also:

     * Support Catalogs

     * Save Prefs

     * Easy-of-use_Interface

     * Preference Editor very easy

     * Change options you dont need in the Prefs

     * If you forget the colon after a DiskDrive, AssignerPro will do it
     for you!

     * Its For Free!! Send me an E-mail and you get registered

     * it has a nice Logo

  Thats all!!


@endnode
 

